data.description: Nestled in the picturesque community of Cool Water , this exquisite 5-bedroom home boasts an open concept design, high ceilings, and luxurious finishes throughout. With a gourmet-style kitchen, multiple living areas, great natural lighting, and a tranquil backyard, this residence offers the perfect blend of modern elegance and comfort. Don't miss the opportunity to make this impeccable 5-bedroom home your own. Experience luxury living with modern conveniences in a serene and picturesque setting. Schedule a showing today and discover your dream home in Cool Water!
